apify.description:
ALC Lawyers is a boutique law firm based in Sydney with a focus on Australian immigration law. Our clients have the confidence that their Australian immigration needs are fully met in the complex and ever-changing Australian migration environment. Our lawyers and Registered Migration Agents have over 15 years of experience in the industry, specialising in:

- Global Talent Independent (GTI) visa programme
- Corporate migration, including Employer Nomination Scheme and Temporary Skills Shortage visa programmes;
- Business Innovation and Investment Programme, including 2 year reviews for Subclass 132 visas holders;
- General Skilled Migration, including skills assessment and points test; 
- Family migration, including Partner and Parent migration;
- Complex matters including LGBTQIA+ clients, as well as health, character, and integrity waivers; and
- Administrative Appeals Tribunal process and proceedings.

We provide our clients with EXPERT advice, based on years of valuable EXPERIENCE, with fast and reliable service EXCELLENCE. 

Please get in contact with us, by emailing info@alclawyers.com.au, if you’re looking to migrate to, or extend your stay in, Australia.
